text: Jiří Kulhánek (born 8 March 1996) is a Czech footballer who plays for Mladá Boleslav on loan from Sparta Prague as a defensive midfielder. ==Club career== ===Slovan Liberec=== Kulhánek made his professional debut for Slovan Liberec against Fastav Zlín on 30 July 2017.SLOVAN LIBEREC VS.
